The King's Speech Jadi Raja di Oscar 2011. Selengkapnya di http://bit.ly/gbtQTg
Thank you for all followers! We hope you enjoy the 83rd Academy Awards, just like we do. Have a nice day! :)
Alas, the Oscar for Best Motion Picture is The King's Speech! Congrats! Winning four Oscars in total!
Steven Spielberg is up presenting Best Motion Picture! We love the Jurassic Park theme song as background as he walk on stage.
Or Inception? The King's Speech? The Fighter? True Grit? The Social Network? The Kids Are All Right? Winter's Bone? Tough choice!
And there is only one nomination left! Who do you think will win Best Picture at tonight's #Oscars? Black Swan? Toy Story 3? 127 Hours?
And the Academy Award for Best Actor goes to Colin Firth (The King's Speech). Long live the king! :P
Sandra Bullock (previous Best Actress winner) present Best Actor nominees..
But there will be only one winner. And the winner for Best Actress is... Natalie Portman! Congratulations mom-to-be!
The nominees are Annette Bening, Nicole Kidman, Jennifer Lawrence, Natalie Portman and Michelle Williams.
Jeff Bridges is now presenting #Oscars five Best Actress nominees..
Dan pemenang Best Achievement in Directing adalah Tom Hooper untuk film The King's Speech!
Up now.. Best Achievement in Directing..
The Best Original Song Winner is Randy Newman "We Belong Together" for Toy Story 3! We love you Randy!
The Best Original Song is next! Who'll win? The song from Toy Story 3, 127 Hours, Tangled or Country Strong?
And.. congrats for Angus Wall and Kirk Baxter (The Social Network) for Best Film Editing!
Also presented by Jude Law and Robert Downey, Jr., nominees for Best Film Editing...
And the Oscar for Best Visual Effects goes to Inception (Paul Franklin, Chris Corbould, Andrew Lockley and Peter Bebb)
And the Oscar for Best Documentary (Feature) goes to Inside Job. Congratulations Charles Ferguson and Audrey Marrs!
Wow! Oprah Winfrey presenting #Oscars for Feature Documentary.
Best Short Film (Live Action): God of Love (Luke Matheny) He surely is surprised to be the winner. Awww.. Congratulations!
Pemenang Best Documentary (Short Subject) adalah Strangers No More (Karen Goodman dan Kirk Simon)
Best Costume Design: Colleen Atwood (Alice in Wonderland) Undoubtedly!
Best Makeup dimenangkan oleh The Wolfman (Rick Baker dan Dave Elsey)
Best Sound Mixing Oscar Winner is Lira Hirschberg, Gary A. Rizzo and Ed Novick for Inception.. Nice!
Oscar Winner for Sound Editing is Richard King (Inception)
Best Original Score is the second Oscar for The Social Network today!
Dan lagi-lagi The Social Network (Trent Reznor dan Atticus Ross) memenangkan Oscar. Kali ini Best Original Score! Congrats!
Lagi2 nominasinya terdiri dari 127 Hours, The Social Network, The King's Speech, Inception dan How to Train Your Dragon...
Nicole Kidman and Hugh Jackman present #Oscars for Original Score...
Christian Bale (The Fighter) for Best Supporting Actor. He surely deserves the Oscar!
And the winner of Best Supporting Actor is....
Nominees of Actor in a Supporting Role: Christian Bale, John Hawkes, Jeremy Renner, Mark Ruffalo and Geoffrey Rush.
And the winner for Best Foreign Language film is In a Better World from Denmark! Congrats!
Nominations of foreign language film: Biutiful, Dogtooth, In a Better World, Incendies and Outside the Law..
Oh my, Anne Hathaway wear Tuxedo and James Franco wear a dress..
Dan pemenang Best Original Screenplay adalah David Seidler (The King's Speech)
The winner of Best Adapted Screenplay is The Social Network (Aaron Sorkin).
Javier Bardem and Josh Brolin wearing all white suits presenting Best Screenplay..
There are only 3 nominators for this category, and the winner is the lovable family movie, Toy Story 3 (Lee Unkrich). :)
Also presented by JT and Mila Kunis, Best Animated Feature Film..
And the Oscar for Best Short Film goes to The Lost Thing (Shaun Tan and Andrew Ruhemann)
Justin Timberlake and Mila Kunis is now presenting Oscar for Best Short Film.
@pinknotpunk no, we're watching it live.. :)
The winner of Best Supporting Actress is Melissa Leo (The Fighter). Yg sdh ntn filmnya must know the reason why, yg blm ntn, ayo nonton! :)
Oscar for Cinematography goes to Wally Pfister for Inception.. No wonder.. Such a mindblowing cinematography!
Pemenang Oscar kategori Art Direction & Cinematography adalah Robert Stromberg & Karen O' Hara (Alice in Wonderland). Congratulations!
James Franco dan Anne Hathaway sebagai host Oscars membawa keluarganya hadir. James membawa Ibu dan Neneknya, Anne membawa Ibunya.
It's time for the 83rd Annual Academy Awards #Oscars
